*.apk
*.zip
*.pdf
*.keystore
*.jks
*.p12
*_keystore*
# Cellebrite / device extractions and any serial-named dumps
R5CT*/
R5CT*
# Extracted APK working folders
SecureFolder/
com.samsung.*/
com.sec.*/
*_apk/
*base_*.apk/

